{"tid":871341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新手請工人，有咩要注意","createTime":"2018-10-22T00:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T14:25:01.000Z","uid":57505,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4f52ba6e65623dc23b7e03c55a99a68686a538d1","tid":871341,"uid":57505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"姐姐啱啱嚟咗幾日<br />\n開始講開放假問題<br />\n我地就諗住放佢閒日<br />\n佢就話想放星期日<br />\n我地本身都係返開 shift <br />\n所以唔一定星期日放假<br />\n<br />\n不過佢講到自己冇朋友好慘<br />\n希望可以星期日放<br />\n咁我地就話唔 guarantee 一定放你星期日，不過盡量啦<br />\n佢又話 ok<br />\n<br />\n其實生活細節上仲有咩要注意？<br />\n應當佢一家人<br />\n定係對佢好嚴厲苛刻？"},{"pid":"d577d6fbd14c346146f032fddcbb10a514dc9828","tid":871341,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"人地離開別井都好慘，俾少少錢唔係大哂<br />\n有返d同理心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知你點解要同姐姐一齊放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通你放weekday想同姐姐玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa76cdc90e477faf23223dc89ff3e7df21394e3","tid":871341,"uid":34759,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d577d6fbd14c346146f032fddcbb10a514dc9828","tid":871341,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"人地離開別井都好慘，俾少少錢唔係大哂<br />\n有返d同理心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知你點解要同姐姐一齊放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通你放weekday想同姐姐玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":