":"啲工人離鄉別井已經好慘 仲要寄人籬下<br />\n樓豬應該一個星期俾返兩三日假佢同啲朋友相聚下  盡可能都唔好要佢打掃 有能力嘅咪自己做返囉 <br />\n煮飯個啲辛苦嘢就唔好要人做啦 簡簡單單出街食 <br />\n請得工人就要俾多啲愛心 <br />\n如果唔係等飲經血湯啦"},{"pid":"6dacda1334ccc7ec27a9e15c7490318efb3a1346","tid":871341,"uid":57505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b40167625f2631f423221dd7551fab808bcf4d5","tid":871341,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"有小朋友？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:27:44.000Z","msg":"係，有兩個"},{"pid":"51ac0e77763c2f43e77da68e77d3e8813f376476","tid":871341,"uid":57505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5ecfa9707cb5d886ac851ce074a03b9ea49e06b1","tid":871341,"uid":54359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fa76cdc90e477faf23223dc89ff3e7df21394e3","tid":871341,"uid":34759,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d577d6fbd14c346146f032fddcbb10a514dc9828","tid":871341,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"人地離開別井都好慘，俾少少錢唔係大哂<br />\n有返d同理心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知你點解要同姐姐一齊放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通你放weekday想同姐姐玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:28:51.000Z","msg":"樓主意思係 如果佢兩公婆星期日放唔到假 姐姐又放假 咁邊個做屋企野<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔明？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:38:42.000Z","msg":"你點知樓主係兩公婆組合？<br />\n屋企做少日家務就唔掂？<br />\n<br />\n樓主絕對有權俾工人放平日，不過工人始終入屋，盡可能都為佢設想下<br />\n你對人好，人地都會為你賣力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"唔係做唔做家務咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n係有兩個好細嘅小朋友要照顧<br />\n<br />\n我一開始講咗我地兩個都係返 shift <br />\n<br />\n你睇清楚先學人答<br />\n<br />\n如果你中學未畢業就直頭唔洗答"},{"pid":"5f5716e6ed427ea0b372f381cb39d067ea806b20","tid":871341,"